Package: linux-headers-avaota${variant:suffix}
Architecture: arm64
Section: kernel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-avaota
Description: Avaota Linux kernel headers
 This package will always depend on the latest Avaota Linux
 kernel headers available.

Package: linux-image-avaota${variant:suffix}
Architecture: arm64
Section: kernel
Provides: ${dkms:zfs-modules} ${dkms:wireguard-linux-compat-modules}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-avaota, linux-firmware
Description: Avaota Linux kernel image
 This package will always depend on the latest Avaota Linux
 kernel image available.

Package: linux-tools-avaota${variant:suffix}
Architecture: arm64
Section: kernel
Provides: linux-tools
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-tools-${kernel-abi-version}-avaota
Description: Avaota Linux kernel tools
 This package will always depend on the latest Avaota Linux
 kernel tools available.

Package: linux-avaota${variant:suffix}
Architecture: arm64
Section: kernel
Provides: ${test:provides-full-avaota} ${test:provides-full-preferred}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-avaota${variant:suffix} (= ${binary:Version}), linux-headers-avaota${variant:suffix} (= ${binary:Version})
Recommends: linux-tools-${kernel-abi-version}-avaota, ubuntu-kernel-accessories
Description: Complete Avaota Linux kernel and headers
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Avaota Linux
 kernel and headers available.
